                                                            <div class="vs-portfolio-heading__inner">
                                                                <h3 class="vs-portfolio-title"><span>Om at home - Wellness App</span>
                                                                </h3>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <p class="vs-portfolio-heading-desccription">Om At Home is an app dedicated to helping trauma survivors through mindfulness classes. This app helps users to experience the power of community healing through their live-streamed meditation classes. Their mindfulness guides use techniques and language tailored specifically for the needs of the community. This app offers in app purchase, subscriptions and free trials.</p>

                                                        <div class="vs-portfolio-body">
                                                            <div class="vs-portfolio-info">
                                                                <div class="vs-portfolio-info-item">
